---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Government & Defense Solutions"
  description="Secure audio and video solutions for federal, defense, and municipal applications. Clearance-ready, Made in USA."
>
  <section class="bg-primary text-white py-20">
    <div class="container-default">
      <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Government & Defense</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 max-w-3xl">
        Trusted by NASA, US military, and federal agencies since 1994. Our technology has
        been deployed in some of the most secure and mission-critical environments in the world.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-default">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Government Agencies Choose Pragmatic</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Made in USA</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">All products manufactured in Santa Clara County, California. TAA compliant options available.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Security Clearance Ready</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Our team can work with cleared contractors and comply with facility security requirements.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">NASA Heritage</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Developed wireless video technology for NASA's Mars Rover prototype at Ames Research Center.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary mr-3 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Long-Term Support</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Extended product lifecycles and long-term technical support for mission-critical installations.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Notable Government Projects</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">NASA Ames Research Center</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Wireless video transmission for Mars Rover prototype testing</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">US Coast Guard</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Communication systems for vessels and facilities</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Nuclear Power Facilities</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Secure audio and video distribution systems</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold">Military Installations</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Facility-wide paging and announcement systems</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">Solutions for Government Applications</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Secure Communications</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">PA systems, paging, and emergency notification</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Facility Audio</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Distributed audio for cafeterias, gyms, common areas</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Directional Systems</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Focused audio for exhibits and visitor centers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 section-padding">
    <div class="container-default text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Discuss Your Government Project</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Our team understands government procurement processes and can work within your
        requirements. Contact us to discuss your specific needs.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/quote" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
